title: Louisiana Baked Beef Fillet Steak with Herb-Roasted Veggies, Slaw & Dilly-Parsley Mayo
description: Load up beef steak with flavour before baking it until golden and tender. Smokey, Southern-inspired, Louisiana spice blend and a creamy dill-parsley slaw will combine to make a sensational dinner that everyone will happily devour!
